ked by Rs 400 crore seed capital, these projects aim to boost planned urban development. The land-pooling model is being adopted, transforming farmers into development partners.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/varanasi-development-authority-unveils-three-major-townships-after-32-years/131600350?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-29398/131600350.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}